Rules for Astro page components.
- Implement SEO best practices: use <title>, <meta>, sitemap, and robots.txt.
- Defer JavaScript when possible (`client:idle`, `client:visible`).
- Use clean and semantic route names (e.g., about.astro, index.astro).
- Use Island Architecture properly.
- Only hydrate interactivity when absolutely necessary.
- Avoid `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` unless content is properly sanitized.
- Include SEO meta tags per page:
  ---
  import { Meta } from '@/components/Meta.astro';
  ---
  <Meta title="Page Title" description="SEO description here" />
